{"tid":1378842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 美孚有鬼","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:18.000Z","uid":266229,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e519189aa26716e3238de4c460b884b3272ca3d3","tid":1378842,"uid":266229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:49:49.000Z","msg":"啱啱返屋企經過美孚喺荃灣綫行緊去西鐵站<br />\n中途 行行下對面有幾個企左喺度嘅人同我講野<br />\n<br />\n👨🏽=佢👷🏻&zwj;♂️=我<br />\n<br />\n👨🏽:係唔係啱啱發完夢<br />\n👷🏻&zwj;♂️:下...下....冇啊<br />\n<br />\n咁我又冇口罩又唔係黑衫，佢冇講野就走左<br />\n佢語氣又唔似幫我 又冇乜野拎住 所以有啲懷疑<br />\n大家小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a817eafb1683984d99a7cd03f68091c7a9e653","tid":1378842,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5317e568fcf380e5d08596e16b7bbc60214d0d64","tid":1378842,"uid":266229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e18f754a99b227ae4f7bfb003ba02199118c924c","tid":1378842,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:52:30.000Z","msg":"大家保護自己最重要<br />\n唔好同陌生人講野"},{"pid":"25ecd906e7a3ce3ce6b849a1e6ae450f490df81b","tid":1378842,"uid":266229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:53:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a563acbca0881dc973112443fd6bd8a1e551ff1","tid":1378842,"uid":266229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3066c766ece6ac4d58031a670b0e5a4abee4c1fc","tid":1378842,"uid":287410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19fb46c61ffe87f327ddc6a9b7762fe4a9416cd","tid":1378842,"uid":1992